# Just Cars API

### Docker services:
  - api (main)
  - postgres (database)
  - elasticsearch (simple search)
  - sidekiq (for active storage, async elasticsearch[future])
  - redis (for sidekiq)

### Some information about API
 - uses Elasticsearch for search offers
 - uses simple JWT token authentication
 - allows to store images in AWS S3
 - price is implemented as a Integer(cents) [1000 == 10.00 zl]
 - ...
 - TODO Rspec


## Start-up
```sh
$ docker-compose build
$ docker-compose up
Ctrl + c [stop server]
```
or
```sh
$ docker-compose build
$ docker-compose start
$ docker-compose stop [stop server]
```
## Setup data
This command create user, its offer and index in elasticsearch.
```sh
$ docker-compose run api rake db:create db:migrate db:seed
```

# Requests

### Create token
```sh
curl -X POST http://localhost:3000/v1/user_token \
  -H 'Content-Type: application/json' \
  -d '{
    "auth": {
        "email": "user@justcars.pl",
        "password": "justcars123"
    }
}'
```
Response
```sh
{
  "jwt": "eyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJleHAiOjE1ODIzMjc5NjYsInN1YiI6N30.wlRZ4Xd1fLUBVVELPS4GLWNZx-FtAtijU2LWeLuOzq4"
}
```

### Create offer
```sh
curl -X POST http://localhost:3000/v1/offers \
  -H 'Authorization: eyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJleHAiOjE1ODIzMjkzMzcsInN1YiI6N30.nYMH3aH3otyxEPj4gfQRK1MeuVchZh3c3EWh5pVP-B4' \
  -H 'Content-Type: application/json' \
  -d '{
  "title": "bmw f30",
  "description": "bmw seria 320 f30",
  "price": "227000",
  "image": "data:image/jpeg;base64,"
}'
```
Response
```sh
{

}
```

### Search params

API allows to use these params for endpoint GET http://localhost:3000/v1/offers

| name | example |
| ------ | ------ |
| id | ?id=100 |
| title | ?title=bmw 320i |
| description | ?description=model g20 M Sport |
| price_gteq | ?price_gteq=100000 |
| price_lteq | ?price_lteq=235000 |

| name | options | example |
| ------ |------| ------ |
| sort_by  | [id, title, description, price], default: id | ?sort_by=id |
| sort_order | [asc, desc], default: asc | ?sort_order=desc |

| name | options | example |
| ------ |------| ------ |
| per_page  | default: 30, min: 1, max: 100 | ?per_page=50 |
| page | default: 1 | ?page=4 |
